            <div class="column small-five small-push-one reset last">
                <div class="boxcontent">
                    <h2><strong>OVERVIEW</strong> </h2>
                    <p><p>The Huracán EVO RWD delivers the evolution of the most successful Lamborghini V10 to the realm of pure, unfiltered driving emotion, where skill and engineering excellence combine to deliver an exhilarating experience. As the driver, you exercise greater control over the car to form a unique and intimate bond: Rewind to Rear-Wheel Drive means a return to the origins of mechanical purity, the true essence of a Lamborghini.</p>
</p>
                                                        </div>
            </div>
            <div class="image-mobile hidden-over-small"><div style="background-image:url(https://www.lamborghini.com/sites/it-en/files/DAM/lamborghini/model/huracan/huracan-evo-rwd/new/overview-right.jpg)"></div></div>
        </section>


        <section id="block1" class="stripe row-content block1 fullwidth">
            <div class="images">
                

<svg id="block1" class="skew" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-labelledby="desc">
                <desc></desc>            <svg viewBox="0 0 1.5 1" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice">
                <clipPath id="block1-mask">
