                                                </ul><ul class="content_4 tabcontent" >
                          <h5 class="hidden-over-medium">WHEELS</h5>
                                                        <li><h4 class="label">front rims</h4><span class="data">19&#039;&#039; ; 8.5J x 19 ET 42</span><div style="clear:both"></div></li>
                                                        <li><h4 class="label">rear rims</h4><span class="data">19&#039;&#039; ; 11Jx19 ET 40</span><div style="clear:both"></div></li>
                                                        <li><h4 class="label">front tiers</h4><span class="data">245/35 Z R19</span><div style="clear:both"></div></li>
                                                        <li><h4 class="label">rear tiers</h4><span class="data">305/35Z R19</span><div style="clear:both"></div></li>
                                                </ul><ul class="content_5 tabcontent" >
                          <h5 class="hidden-over-medium">STEERING AND SUSPENSION</h5>
                                                        <li><h4 class="label">control system</h4><span class="data">Electronic Stability Control (integrating ABS and TCS)</span><div style="clear:both"></div></li>
                                                        <li><h4 class="label">SUSPENSION TYPE</h4><span class="data">Double wishbone fully independent suspension</span><div style="clear:both"></div></li>
                                                        <li><h4 class="label">steering system</h4><span class="data">Electro-mechanical Power Steering (EPS)</span><div style="clear:both"></div></li>
                                                </ul><ul class="content_6 tabcontent" >
                          <h5 class="hidden-over-medium">BRAKING SYSTEM</h5>
                                                        <li><h4 class="label">brakes</h4><span class="data">Cast iron brakes with fixed monoblock calipers with 8 pistons (front) and 4 pistons (rear), in aluminum, iron disks</span><div style="clear:both"></div></li>
                                                </ul><ul class="content_7 tabcontent" >
                          <h5 class="hidden-over-medium">SAFETY</h5>
